OL,3,CGodmother of 10-year-old stabbed 11
OL,4,Ctimes by her mum 'disgusted'
OL,6,FThe godmother of a 10-year-old girl
OL,7,Fwho was fatally stabbed by her mother
OL,8,Fhas told ITV News Central how she
OL,9,Ffeels justice has not been served
OL,10,Fafter a murder trial did not take
OL,11,Fplace.
OL,13,FKayleigh Colclough spoke to ITV News
OL,14,FCentral Reporter Ravneet Nandra at
OL,15,FShay's favourite place to play outside
OL,16,F- Lightwoods Park & House in Bearwood.
OL,18,FShe said Shay "was my world and when
OL,19,Fshe was taken away, it broke me."
