OL,6,FMs Colclough co-parented Shay with
OL,7,FJasmine for the first five years of
OL,8,FShay's life and took them into her
OL,9,Fhome after they left their previous
OL,10,Faccommodation with Shay's father.
OL,12,FShe also reflected on what it was like
OL,13,Fwhen she found out Shay was killed by
OL,14,Fher mother, telling ITV News: "I never
OL,15,Fthought she would kill Shay.
OL,17,F"I have no words for her, she doesn't
OL,18,Fexist to me anymore," she added.
