OL,6,FHer comments come as Shay's mother,
OL,7,Fwho is from Rowley Regis, has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,9,Forder after she pleaded guilty to
OL,10,Fmanslaughter on the basis of
OL,11,Fdiminished responsibility in August.
OL,13,FShay died as a result of stab wounds
OL,14,Fto the chest.
OL,16,FJaskirat Kaur, also known as Jasmine,
OL,17,Fhas previously admitted the
OL,18,Fmanslaughter of Shay Kang on the basis
OL,19,Fof diminished responsibility.
