OL,6,FIn a wide-ranging interview with ITV
OL,7,FNews Central Reporter Ravneet Nandra,
OL,8,FMs Colclough reminisces on what it was
OL,9,Flike looking after Shay and the joy
OL,10,Fshe brought her.
OL,12,FShe said: "Even at the first scan,
OL,13,Fthat first heartbeat, I fell in love
OL,14,Fwith her, before adding: "It was me
OL,15,Fthat was providing for her and she
OL,16,Fjust made me happy."
OL,18,FShe continued: "That smile just got me
OL,19,Fthrough the day. Everything I did, I
OL,20,Fdid for Shay."
