OL,6,F"Her aura was bright."
OL,8,F"She was my world and when she was
OL,9,Ftaken away, it broke me."
OL,11,FMs Colclough also told ITV News how
OL,12,Fshe began to see changes in Jasmine's
OL,13,Fmood and had even hit Shay when she
OL,14,Fwas little.
OL,16,F"She had become toxic, narcissistic,
OL,17,Fabusive, moody, always jealous of
OL,18,FShay."
