OL,6,FMs Colclough also describes her
OL,7,Ffrustration of when she found out
OL,8,Fabout the killing, telling ITV News:
OL,9,F"I screamed, I was angry, I punched
OL,10,Fthe wall.
OL,12,F"For the first eight weeks, I didn't
OL,13,Fknow who I was."
OL,15,F"I never thought she would kill Shay.
OL,16,FI don't know what happened."
OL,18,F"I have no words for her, she doesn't
OL,19,Fexist to me anymore."
