OL,6,FIf there was a court trial, Ms
OL,7,FColclough said she's confident Jasmine
OL,8,Fwould not have received a manslaughter
OL,9,Fsentence on the basis of diminished
OL,10,Fresponsibility.
OL,12,F"I think every child deserves a voice
OL,13,Fand Shay didn't get one."
OL,15,F"There's so much that people don't
OL,16,Fknow in the five years she lived with
OL,17,Fme."
