OL,6,F"In trial, I would have got that out
OL,7,Fand done my best to try and speak up
OL,8,Fto Shay and get the justice she
OL,9,Fdeserved."
OL,11,F"To me, it's disgusting."
OL,13,F"If you've got parents like Jas
OL,14,Fbringing children up, what chance have
OL,15,Fthese children got? It's down to the
OL,16,Fparents too. Step up...be a mum, be a
OL,17,Fdad.
OL,19,F"Children are our future."
